### 9.1 MVP Definition

The MVP demonstrates core AI value: an SME can enter their expenses, receive AI-generated priority recommendations with explanations, and view cash flow status — all within a polished, responsive dashboard.

### MVP (Now) v1.1 (3 Months) v2.0 (6 Months)

*   Manual expense input
*   Cash flow prediction (30-day)
